{"tid":1163511,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"牛市之全地球都需要一場石油危機","createTime":"2019-05-20T13:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T01:10:59.000Z","uid":40478,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7921699e87c4c81acfb8d035ad4ffbe057e010fb","tid":1163511,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:11:44.000Z","msg":"上回樓主講到只要石油危機發生，支那既通脹就會失控<br />\n而對美帝黎講，石油危機係百利無害<br />\n因為美帝已經係產油國，如果歐亞大陸失去產油區，歐亞國家既工業都會受重創，而有相對平既石油既美帝工業就會得益<br />\n所以對美國黎講，消滅伊朗，一統中東，挾石油以令諸侯自然係最好，但其實一場搞串成個波斯灣場既戰爭亦係大大有利<br />\n支那國呢家日日播抗美援朝電影唔係純粹打下飛機，而係因為支那國好可能不得不又要打一場必輸無疑既抗美援伊戰爭，如果支那戰敗，伊朗滅亡，支那就會因為無石油而仆街，而就算支那奇蹟地打成僵持之局，一樣會因為國內通脹不可控而仆街<br />\n<br />\n利申：牛軍諸葛孔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f755cc45051bab035d35f520bb041a6a085e157","tid":1163511,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"咁早就出隆上對 邊有人睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e9842578f681013a0ff2e989e2b3d15cfd2d5c","tid":1163511,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f755cc45051bab035d35f520bb041a6a085e157","tid":1163511,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"咁早就出隆上對 邊有人睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"隆中呀青<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef74567aa93ff783f8df407ca051e45da4d7536","tid":1163511,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"叫委內瑞拉幫幫手"},{"pid":"640ec5e843f41956e832f2005e5d7a029ee33ab6","tid":1163511,"uid":186177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:33:54.000Z","msg":"俾人發現係九方狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0792614e0932923259af2e07c6f9f6f1312228ac","tid":1163511,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T01:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}